OL,3,CActor Eddie Redmayne landed with
OL,4,C#1,500 court bill after speeding in
OL,5,C20mph zone
OL,7,FHollywood star Eddie Redmayne has been
OL,8,Flanded with a #1,530 court bill after
OL,9,Fhe was caught breaking one of London's
OL,10,F20mph speed limits.
OL,12,FThe Oscar-winning actor faced a
OL,13,Fcriminal prosecution from the
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police over an offence
OL,15,Fcommitted last October on the A4
OL,16,Fthrough Earl's Court.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
