OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776269466
OL,3,CActor Eddie Redmayne landed with
OL,4,C#1,500 court bill after speeding in
OL,5,C20mph zone
OL,7,FCourt papers show Redmayne's Audi was
OL,8,Fclocked by a speed camera at 28mph as
OL,9,Fhe drove towards West Kensington at
OL,10,Fjust before 11am on October 14 last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe Day of the Jackal star admitted
OL,14,Fbeing the speeding driver, but
OL,15,Fsubmitted the form to the police too
OL,16,Flate to avoid a criminal prosecution.
OL,18,FHe pleaded guilty to the offence, and
OL,19,Fwas sentenced last Wednesday at a
OL,20,Fprivate court hearing to a #1,000 fine.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
