OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776269466
OL,3,CActor Eddie Redmayne landed with
OL,4,C#1,500 court bill after speeding in
OL,5,C20mph zone
OL,7,FRedmayne received three penalty points
OL,8,Fon his licence, and must also pay #130
OL,9,Fin costs and a #400 victim surcharge.
OL,11,FThe actor, who won an Academy Award in
OL,12,F2015 for his portrayal of Stephen
OL,13,FHawking in The Theory of Everything,
OL,14,Fwas not required to attend court, as
OL,15,Fhis case was dealt with at Westminster
OL,16,FMagistrates' Court through the Single
OL,17,FJustice Procedure.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
