CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776269466
OL,3,CActor Eddie Redmayne landed with
OL,4,C#1,500 court bill after speeding in
OL,5,C20mph zone
OL,7,FKensington and Chelsea Council
OL,8,Fannounced in 2020 that it planned to
OL,9,Fintroduce a 20mph limit to all its
OL,10,Fresidential roads.
OL,12,FThe A4 Cromwell Road, where Redmayne
OL,13,Fwas caught out, became a 20mph limit
OL,14,Fin autumn 2023 as part of a Transport
OL,15,Ffor London initiative to lower speeds
OL,16,Fon 65 kilometres of London's roads.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
