FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776269466
OL,3,CActor Eddie Redmayne landed with
OL,4,C#1,500 court bill after speeding in
OL,5,C20mph zone
OL,7,FThe Met submitted evidence including
OL,8,Fan image of Redmayne's speeding Audi,
OL,9,Fand said the star had been sent a
OL,10,Fnotice of intended prosecution on
OL,11,FOctober 20 last year, six days after
OL,12,Fthe offence.
OL,14,FThe court records show Redmayne
OL,15,Fresponded on March 1 this year,
OL,16,Fsigning a form agreeing that he had
OL,17,Fbeen the driver that day.
OL,19,FBut a police official told the court
OL,20,Fthat his form had not arrived in time
OL,21,Fto avoid a court case.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1776269466
OL,3,CActor Eddie Redmayne landed with
OL,4,C#1,500 court bill after speeding in
OL,5,C20mph zone
OL,7,F"Due to the Late response to notice of
OL,8,Fintended prosecution, this case does
OL,9,Fnot qualify for an out of court
OL,10,Fdisposal and has therefore been
OL,11,Freferred to the prosecutions team for
OL,12,Fa single justice procedure notice to
OL,13,Fbe issued," she wrote.
OL,15,FRedmayne was among 450 motorists to be
OL,16,Fprosecuted by the Met last week for
OL,17,Fbreaking one of London's 20mph zones,
OL,18,Fresulting in court fines ranging from
OL,19,F#40 to the maximum #1,000 penalty.
